title: X-Men v4 (2013) (Tablet Edition)
description:
I adjusted the resolution and compression of the original scan for easier reading on tablets and to save space. All credit goes to the original scanner for their hard work. I have added 'Tablet Edition' to the name to avoid confusion.

Enjoy and please seed back.



X-Men 5

By:   	Brian Wood, David Lopez, Arthur Adams	
Type:   	Comics
Genres:   	Superhero
Series:   	X-Men
Publisher:   	Marvel Comics	
Pub. Date:  	September 11, 2013
Format:         CBZ

BATTLE OF THE ATOM PART 3! The X-Men and Future X-Men pursue young Scott and Jean. Not all the X-Men agree that the All-New X-Men should be sent back. The cracks in the new all-female X-Men cast start to show.
